[Student "S"]
{You dealt this hand.  

You open with a Weak 2-Bid, 2\H. Partner responds 2NT. What do you say next? 

The 2NT bid is forcing. Your \DK is a feature, but your immediate priority is to let partner know that you have a minimum strength opener, 6, 7 or 8 points. So you rebid 3\H. Partner passes.}

