{You dealt this hand. 
You open with a Weak 2-Bid, 2\S. Partner responds 2NT. What do you say next?
The 2NT bid is forcing. You have 11 points so you cannot reply 3\S. And your suit is not A K Q x x x so you cannot reply 3NT. That means you must bid a "feature" and your \HQ is the best you have. You bid 3\H and partner says 3\S. 

Pass. When you have already described your hand perfectly, partner becomes the Captain.}

