[Auction "E"]
1H 2S 3H 4S X pass pass pass
{You should jump to 4\S, hoping to shut them out of their \H slam. As you can see they have at most one \S loser. Down 4 doubled for your side is much better than letting them bid and make a slam. Of course we know they should have continued bidding, but opponents sometimes make mistakes.}

