{One of the characteristics of Weak 2-Bids is that Responder often is unsure how high to go. That's why the 2NT bid is such a great tool. In this case you bid 2NT and partner says 3\H.  

Well, you weren't sure whether to take partner to game or not, so when he says he has a minimum hand you have to pass.}

